f90882a72db3"],

Cell["\<\
This notebook gives us the numerical solution of the scattering response of \
the cavity in the given electromechanical system. The electromechanical \
device is given by the standard optomechanical Hamiltonian with the addition \
of a Kerr non-linearity in the cavity mode. The equations of motion are used \
from the paper \[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]Self sustained oscillations for a Kerr \
non-linear electromechanical system\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote].\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{3.9554423760688057`*^9, 
  3.955592215362451*^9},ExpressionUUID->"95f34d6c-bc9b-4593-96eb-\
dd68a3110195"],

